{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Alset: TRS"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"f5e8cb3a-ade2-5ae7-b3fc-920320e88883","excerpt":"An evening of insightful coversation and lively activities took place as Prof Y.C. Tay hosted ALSET for Fellow's Tea at the cosy Master's Common Lounge inâ€¦","html":"<p>An evening of insightful coversation and lively activities took place as Prof Y.C. Tay hosted ALSET for Fellow's Tea at the cosy Master's Common Lounge in Tembusu College.</p>\n<p>The attentive and inquiring Tembusians warmed up quickly to Mr Kevin Hartman, Translational Research Coordinator, as he describes how the 3 branches of ALSET work together in making a difference for the NUS community and Singapore.</p>\n<p>\n  <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n  \n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ce1f8acb3306989e5f54eeec15330776/d53fe/200219fellowtea1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"audience seated in Tembusu College Master's Common Lounge\"\n        title=\"The ambience at the Master's Common Lounge provided for stimulating discussion. Mr Hartman (centre right) with Prof Tay (right)\"\n        src=\"/static/ce1f8acb3306989e5f54eeec15330776/1697e/200219fellowtea1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ce1f8acb3306989e5f54eeec15330776/a2cfd/200219fellowtea1.jpg 148w,\n/static/ce1f8acb3306989e5f54eeec15330776/3348f/200219fellowtea1.jpg 295w,\n/static/ce1f8acb3306989e5f54eeec15330776/1697e/200219fellowtea1.jpg 590w,\n/static/ce1f8acb3306989e5f54eeec15330776/6a00a/200219fellowtea1.jpg 885w,\n/static/ce1f8acb3306989e5f54eeec15330776/46304/200219fellowtea1.jpg 1180w,\n/static/ce1f8acb3306989e5f54eeec15330776/d53fe/200219fellowtea1.jpg 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">The ambience at the Master's Common Lounge provided for stimulating discussion. Mr Hartman (centre right) with Prof Tay (right)</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p>As the session continued, an engaging conversation took place around how the data collected within ALSET's Data Lake can help resolve pertinent challenging issues faced by NUS students.</p>\n<p>Mr Hartman made sure to highlight that the mock data accessible by students places them in a good position to take action and find solutions to the challenges they encounter on campus. To demonstrate this, Mr Hartman engaged the students in an experiential Design Thinking exercise.</p>\n<p>\n  <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n  \n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4956ff2e98248d93919164f275db5f86/d53fe/200219fellowtea2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Mr Hartman engages students as they work on a list of challenges\"\n        title=\"Mr Hartman engages students as they brainstorm in groups on challenges they face\"\n        src=\"/static/4956ff2e98248d93919164f275db5f86/1697e/200219fellowtea2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4956ff2e98248d93919164f275db5f86/a2cfd/200219fellowtea2.jpg 148w,\n/static/4956ff2e98248d93919164f275db5f86/3348f/200219fellowtea2.jpg 295w,\n/static/4956ff2e98248d93919164f275db5f86/1697e/200219fellowtea2.jpg 590w,\n/static/4956ff2e98248d93919164f275db5f86/6a00a/200219fellowtea2.jpg 885w,\n/static/4956ff2e98248d93919164f275db5f86/46304/200219fellowtea2.jpg 1180w,\n/static/4956ff2e98248d93919164f275db5f86/d53fe/200219fellowtea2.jpg 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Mr Hartman engages students as they brainstorm in groups on challenges they face</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p>With each group comprising a mix of students of different disciplines and ages, ideas flowed easily and they were soon able to come up with a wide range of challenges.</p>\n<p>Next, another round of interactivity started as the groups were asked to swap lists and each member had to individually rank both the frequency of encounters and importance of surmounting the challenges identified.</p>\n<p>The room was filled with banter as group members discussed each item and clarified any ambiguities with the originating group. Some items brought about chuckles (eg. classes are too early!) while others raised interesting points (eg. lack of core modules to do while student is on internship).</p>\n<p>\n  <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n  \n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ce1f8acb3306989e5f54eeec15330776/d53fe/200219fellowtea1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"audience seated in Tembusu College Master's Common Lounge\"\n        title=\"The groups gathered back for a lively round of interaction\"\n        src=\"/static/ce1f8acb3306989e5f54eeec15330776/1697e/200219fellowtea1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ce1f8acb3306989e5f54eeec15330776/a2cfd/200219fellowtea1.jpg 148w,\n/static/ce1f8acb3306989e5f54eeec15330776/3348f/200219fellowtea1.jpg 295w,\n/static/ce1f8acb3306989e5f54eeec15330776/1697e/200219fellowtea1.jpg 590w,\n/static/ce1f8acb3306989e5f54eeec15330776/6a00a/200219fellowtea1.jpg 885w,\n/static/ce1f8acb3306989e5f54eeec15330776/46304/200219fellowtea1.jpg 1180w,\n/static/ce1f8acb3306989e5f54eeec15330776/d53fe/200219fellowtea1.jpg 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">The groups gathered back for a lively round of interaction</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p>Stretching the groups and their ideas further, Mr Hartman asked each group to retrieve their list of challenges and analyse the ratings given to select one challenge to focus on for prototyping.</p>\n<p>About the Author: <br/>\n<em>Shun works at the ALSET Translation Research Unit as a Research Assistant. Besides writing code in the day, he likes attending meetups and taking long walks.</em></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Fellow's Tea with ALSET@NUS","date":"February 20, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/20feb19FellowTea/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/13feb19talkJS/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"From Game-based Learning to Game Creation @ Talk.js"}},"next":null}}